@startuml
actor Client
participant "User\nService" as UserService
participant "Amazon Auth\nAPI" as Amazon

Client -> UserService: GET /lwa/{region}\n?redirect_uri=...
activate UserService
UserService -> UserService: Validate authenticated user + region
UserService -> UserService: Encrypt state\n(user_id, region, redirect_url)
UserService --> Client: 200 OK + redirectUrl
deactivate UserService

Client -> Amazon: Redirect to\n/ap/oa URL
activate Amazon
Amazon -> Amazon: Authenticate user\n+ collect consent
Amazon --> UserService: GET /lwa/process_token?code=...&state=...
deactivate Amazon

activate UserService
UserService -> UserService: Decrypt and parse state
UserService -> Amazon: Exchange code for\nrefresh token
activate Amazon
Amazon --> UserService: Refresh token
deactivate Amazon

UserService -> UserService: Store refresh token for user + region
UserService --> Client: 302 Redirect to\noriginal redirect_uri
deactivate UserService
@enduml
